Built in 2002
18' clear height

Minutes from Interstate 91, Exits 24 and 25
Office/Industrial zoned

The facility is ideal for tenants seeking to be in a flex, office, retail or service environment in a location within the City of Hartford. The property, designed in a U-shape, has an opening along the rear to access an interior courtyard that contains 12' overhead drive-in doors and a shared loading dock. This property also features private entrances and an 18' clear warehouse. Located in the North Meadows neighborhood, Weston Square has excellent access to downtown Hartford and Interstates 84 and 91.
